==Useful Info==
'''Green draconians''' are the [[poison]]-themed members of the [[list of draconians|draconian]] family, and one of the least threatening if you arrive prepared. Their poison breath attacks deal moderate poison damage and inflict the poison condition each turn you remain in the poison [[cloud]]s they leave behind. They can be found primarily in [[the Realm of Zot]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Poison resistance renders their breath attacks nearly harmless, and they often wind up accidentally poisoning any other draconians in the area. [[Freezing]]-[[brand]]ed weapons help make combat against them much easier.
